high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the fridge on your right.
Pick up lettuce from the fridge.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near sink.
Place lettuce on the sink.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the fridge.
Pick up lettuce from the fridge.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near sink.
Place lettuce on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collecting lettuce from different places and arranging them on a sink.

high_descs: Turn back and head to the fridge.
Pick up the lettuce from the last rack of the fridge.
Turn back and walk across the dining table and turn left towards the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
Turn left and walk, then turn right towards the sink counter top.
Pick up the another lettuce from the sink counter top.
Turn right and walk, then turn left towards the sink.
Put the another lettuce in the back side of the first lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge.
Take out the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn left, head straight to the countertop and then go to the sink to your left.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
Turn left and go to the lettuce on the countertop.
Pick up the lettuce on the countertop.
Go to the sink to your right.
Put the lettuce in the sink behind the one already there.
anns.task_desc: Collect lettuce and put them in a sink.
